  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "c01-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "你知道 AI 智能体为什么宁愿猜错，也不说不知道吗？",
      "gapBefore": 0,
      "audioDuration": 4.08,
      "audioStart": 0,
      "spokenStart": 0.167,
      "spokenEnd": 3.429,
      "actualGapBefore": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "OpenAI 的研究给出一个清楚答案：常见训练和评测，往往更奖励猜中，而不是诚实表达不确定。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.984,
      "audioStart": 3.421,
      "spokenStart": 3.589,
      "spokenEnd": 9.756,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这种激励会把一句顺滑的话，变成错误决策、虚假引用或危险操作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.448,
      "audioStart": 9.755,
      "spokenStart": 9.916,
      "spokenEnd": 14.558,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "你需要分清智能体知道什么、推断什么、又无法验证什么。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.392,
      "audioStart": 14.491,
      "spokenStart": 14.658,
      "spokenEnd": 18.241,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这期会做一张 AI 智能体不确定性与事实核验清单，用来判断问题是否可答、证据标准是什么，以及该回答、核验、澄清还是拒答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 10.2,
      "audioStart": 18.239,
      "spokenStart": 18.401,
      "spokenEnd": 27.796,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "核心方法不是只问答案像不像真的，而是先查问题能否回答，再找高风险事实，并明确什么证据足以改变行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 8.568,
      "audioStart": 27.795,
      "spokenStart": 27.956,
      "spokenEnd": 35.721,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "视频全程干货高价值，让你成为更擅长使用 AI 的人，内容较长，点点关注收藏不迷路。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.576,
      "audioStart": 35.724,
      "spokenStart": 35.881,
      "spokenEnd": 41.653,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "先看猜测激励。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 41.674,
      "spokenStart": 41.833,
      "spokenEnd": 42.824,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章会解释，为什么流畅的 AI 智能体即使不知道事实，也可能因猜测得到更高分。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.504,
      "audioStart": 42.762,
      "spokenStart": 42.924,
      "spokenEnd": 48.617,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "预训练让模型从大量文本中学习语言规律。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.744,
      "audioStart": 48.619,
      "spokenStart": 48.777,
      "spokenEnd": 51.716,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它看到的是流畅陈述，却不会为每个事实同时拿到可靠的真假标签。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.352,
      "audioStart": 51.655,
      "spokenStart": 51.816,
      "spokenEnd": 56.376,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "高频、结构稳定的事实容易学习；",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.168,
      "audioStart": 56.38,
      "spokenStart": 56.536,
      "spokenEnd": 58.902,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "冷门生日、文件名称等任意低频事实，往往没有足够规律让模型补回缺失真相。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.168,
      "audioStart": 58.838,
      "spokenStart": 59.002,
      "spokenEnd": 64.384,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "后训练本应减少错误，但许多评测仍只看准确率。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.176,
      "audioStart": 64.388,
      "spokenStart": 64.544,
      "spokenEnd": 67.913,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "猜对得一分，说不知道却得不到准确率分数。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.72,
      "audioStart": 67.865,
      "spokenStart": 68.013,
      "spokenEnd": 70.943,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "如果模型猜一个生日，它有三百六十五分之一的命中机会；",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.224,
      "audioStart": 70.939,
      "spokenStart": 71.103,
      "spokenEnd": 74.508,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "选择拒答虽然避免自信错误，却保证拿不到命中分。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.224,
      "audioStart": 74.453,
      "spokenStart": 74.608,
      "spokenEnd": 78.044,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "OpenAI 的 SimpleQA 例子更直观：一个模型准确率百分之二十二，错误率百分之二十六，拒答率百分之五十二；",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 7.368,
      "audioStart": 78.044,
      "spokenStart": 78.204,
      "spokenEnd": 84.772,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "另一个准确率只高两点，错误率却达到百分之七十五，几乎从不拒答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.16,
      "audioStart": 84.71,
      "spokenStart": 84.872,
      "spokenEnd": 89.242,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "所以只看准确率会隐藏失败代价。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.048,
      "audioStart": 89.255,
      "spokenStart": 89.402,
      "spokenEnd": 91.668,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "可靠评分应让自信错误付出更高成本，并奖励合适的澄清和拒答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.52,
      "audioStart": 91.606,
      "spokenStart": 91.768,
      "spokenEnd": 96.482,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：第一，流畅生成不会给每个事实附上真假标签。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.968,
      "audioStart": 96.481,
      "spokenStart": 96.642,
      "spokenEnd": 100.812,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，只看准确率会奖励幸运猜测。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.288,
      "audioStart": 100.814,
      "spokenStart": 100.972,
      "spokenEnd": 103.459,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，可靠评测要让自信错误比不确定付出更高代价。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.752,
      "audioStart": 103.459,
      "spokenStart": 103.619,
      "spokenEnd": 107.564,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "检查答案之前，先检查问题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.736,
      "audioStart": 107.592,
      "spokenStart": 107.744,
      "spokenEnd": 109.697,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章帮助 AI 智能体判断，现有信息是否足以给出可靠回答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.064,
      "audioStart": 109.631,
      "spokenStart": 109.797,
      "spokenEnd": 114.058,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "先问四件事：请求是否具体，信息是否可得，事实是否新到不能靠记忆，以及结果能否在行动前核验。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 8.184,
      "audioStart": 114.055,
      "spokenStart": 114.218,
      "spokenEnd": 121.599,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "日期缺失、对象不清或术语含糊，不是推理难题，而是澄清问题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.4,
      "audioStart": 121.595,
      "spokenStart": 121.759,
      "spokenEnd": 126.358,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "智能体应追问真正会改变答案的细节。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.168,
      "audioStart": 126.291,
      "spokenStart": 126.458,
      "spokenEnd": 128.814,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "价格、法规、日程、账户状态和私有记录，只能通过实时或已授权证据回答；",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.36,
      "audioStart": 128.822,
      "spokenStart": 128.974,
      "spokenEnd": 134.542,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "没有访问能力时，正确状态就是未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.192,
      "audioStart": 134.48,
      "spokenStart": 134.642,
      "spokenEnd": 137.035,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "有些问题本来就无法唯一确定。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.616,
      "audioStart": 137.035,
      "spokenStart": 137.195,
      "spokenEnd": 139.018,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "如果多个答案都符合描述，智能体应说明歧义并给出最小选择，而不是编造隐藏意图。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.576,
      "audioStart": 138.96,
      "spokenStart": 139.118,
      "spokenEnd": 144.892,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "低风险头脑风暴可以接受近似答案；",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.976,
      "audioStart": 144.893,
      "spokenStart": 145.052,
      "spokenEnd": 147.228,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "会影响金钱、健康、权限或公开发布的事实，则必须提高证据门槛。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.52,
      "audioStart": 147.159,
      "spokenStart": 147.328,
      "spokenEnd": 152.033,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "当真相无法确定时，拒答不是失败，而是一种受控结果。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.296,
      "audioStart": 152.034,
      "spokenStart": 152.193,
      "spokenEnd": 155.702,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它保护用户，也明确系统缺少哪项信息或工具。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.984,
      "audioStart": 155.642,
      "spokenStart": 155.802,
      "spokenEnd": 158.973,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：第一，检查具体性、可得性、时效性和可核验性。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.376,
      "audioStart": 158.971,
      "spokenStart": 159.133,
      "spokenEnd": 163.697,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，把缺失上下文转成明确的澄清问题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.648,
      "audioStart": 163.694,
      "spokenStart": 163.857,
      "spokenEnd": 166.697,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，把有理由的未知当作有效受控结果。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.504,
      "audioStart": 166.698,
      "spokenStart": 166.857,
      "spokenEnd": 169.566,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "问题可以回答后，还要让不确定性可见。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 3.216,
      "audioStart": 169.582,
      "spokenStart": 169.746,
      "spokenEnd": 172.163,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章把一份顺滑输出拆成事实、推断和未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.104,
      "audioStart": 172.102,
      "spokenStart": 172.263,
      "spokenEnd": 175.563,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "只有存在支持证据时，才能把内容标成已确认事实；",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.32,
      "audioStart": 175.556,
      "spokenStart": 175.723,
      "spokenEnd": 179.232,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "结合假设和判断得出的结论，应明确标成推断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.792,
      "audioStart": 179.178,
      "spokenStart": 179.332,
      "spokenEnd": 182.338,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "使用“已确认”“有支持但不完整”“推断”或“未知”等清楚状态，避免只说“可能”“大概”却不解释缺口。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 7.032,
      "audioStart": 182.336,
      "spokenStart": 182.498,
      "spokenEnd": 188.725,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "置信度要跟随证据覆盖，而不是跟随文案顺滑程度。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.224,
      "audioStart": 188.719,
      "spokenStart": 188.885,
      "spokenEnd": 192.308,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "一份漂亮答案只有一个弱来源，仍然是弱证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.84,
      "audioStart": 192.248,
      "spokenStart": 192.408,
      "spokenEnd": 195.446,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "除非系统真的针对该任务完成校准，否则不要随便给出百分之八十七这类精确数字，虚假精度会遮住真实证据缺口。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 8.52,
      "audioStart": 195.446,
      "spokenStart": 195.606,
      "spokenEnd": 203.314,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "每个重要判断都要连到对应证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.832,
      "audioStart": 203.312,
      "spokenStart": 203.474,
      "spokenEnd": 205.506,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "证据只支持一部分，就缩小判断范围，不要强行拉长引用。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.488,
      "audioStart": 205.445,
      "spokenStart": 205.606,
      "spokenEnd": 209.295,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最后给未知项配一个动作：查一个来源、补一个字段、跑一次检查，或停止高风险操作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.504,
      "audioStart": 209.303,
      "spokenStart": 209.455,
      "spokenEnd": 215.17,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "用户要知道怎样才能消除未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.712,
      "audioStart": 215.113,
      "spokenStart": 215.27,
      "spokenEnd": 217.197,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：第一，区分已确认事实、推断和未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.224,
      "audioStart": 217.197,
      "spokenStart": 217.357,
      "spokenEnd": 220.778,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，让置信度跟随证据覆盖，而不是流畅措辞。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.056,
      "audioStart": 220.78,
      "spokenStart": 220.938,
      "spokenEnd": 224.198,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，为每个重要未知项配一个下一步动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 224.2,
      "spokenStart": 224.358,
      "spokenEnd": 227.039,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "不是每句话都值得投入同样精力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.928,
      "audioStart": 227.062,
      "spokenStart": 227.219,
      "spokenEnd": 229.343,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章告诉你，哪些 AI 智能体事实必须先核验，再进入行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.064,
      "audioStart": 229.276,
      "spokenStart": 229.443,
      "spokenEnd": 233.706,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "先看后果。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 233.705,
      "spokenStart": 233.866,
      "spokenEnd": 234.53,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "涉及金钱、权限、安全、法律、声誉，或难以撤销的操作，都要提高核验等级。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.288,
      "audioStart": 234.476,
      "spokenStart": 234.63,
      "spokenEnd": 240.146,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "优先使用离事实最近的一手来源：账户状态查数据库，规则查官方政策，研究结果查原论文，任务完成查真实产物。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 8.712,
      "audioStart": 240.146,
      "spokenStart": 240.306,
      "spokenEnd": 248.218,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "当单一来源可能过期、偏颇、不完整或被误读时，再找独立证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.256,
      "audioStart": 248.222,
      "spokenStart": 248.378,
      "spokenEnd": 252.832,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "两个页面重复同一句无来源说法，不算两份独立证明。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.248,
      "audioStart": 252.76,
      "spokenStart": 252.932,
      "spokenEnd": 256.36,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "证据必须对应准确判断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.28,
      "audioStart": 256.362,
      "spokenStart": 256.52,
      "spokenEnd": 257.993,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "证明产品存在，不等于证明它具备某个功能；",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.648,
      "audioStart": 257.932,
      "spokenStart": 258.093,
      "spokenEnd": 260.93,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "一项受控实验，也不等于所有场景都必然有效。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.888,
      "audioStart": 260.863,
      "spokenStart": 261.03,
      "spokenEnd": 264.121,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "继续核对日期、范围、对象、单位和例外。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.648,
      "audioStart": 264.131,
      "spokenStart": 264.281,
      "spokenEnd": 267.155,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "很多自信错误，是把真实信息贴到了错误时间、人物或条件上。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.064,
      "audioStart": 267.096,
      "spokenStart": 267.255,
      "spokenEnd": 271.518,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最后，在不可逆行动前设置人工批准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.408,
      "audioStart": 271.526,
      "spokenStart": 271.678,
      "spokenEnd": 274.283,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "智能体可以收集证据和提出建议，但高影响执行必须得到明确授权。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.376,
      "audioStart": 274.223,
      "spokenStart": 274.383,
      "spokenEnd": 278.963,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：第一，按照后果分配事实核验精力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.96,
      "audioStart": 278.962,
      "spokenStart": 279.123,
      "spokenEnd": 282.282,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，优先一手证据，并使用真正独立的交叉核验。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.152,
      "audioStart": 282.279,
      "spokenStart": 282.442,
      "spokenEnd": 285.799,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，在不可逆行动前保留人工批准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.408,
      "audioStart": 285.801,
      "spokenStart": 285.959,
      "spokenEnd": 288.574,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "现在把方法收进一张可复用的 AI 智能体不确定性与事实核验清单，在接受事实答案前逐项检查。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 7.32,
      "audioStart": 288.601,
      "spokenStart": 288.754,
      "spokenEnd": 295.285,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一步是可答性。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 295.285,
      "spokenStart": 295.445,
      "spokenEnd": 296.36,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "记录准确问题、对象、时间范围、时效要求、可用工具，以及会阻塞可靠回答的缺失信息。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.984,
      "audioStart": 296.305,
      "spokenStart": 296.46,
      "spokenEnd": 302.651,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二步是判断清单。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.92,
      "audioStart": 302.657,
      "spokenStart": 302.811,
      "spokenEnd": 303.96,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "把回答拆成会改变决策的重要判断，并分别标记已确认、推断或未知，不把精力浪费在无关措辞上。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 7.248,
      "audioStart": 303.897,
      "spokenStart": 304.06,
      "spokenEnd": 310.512,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三步是证据标准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.992,
      "audioStart": 310.516,
      "spokenStart": 310.672,
      "spokenEnd": 311.866,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "为每个重要判断写清可接受的一手来源、允许时效，以及是否必须独立交叉核验。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.192,
      "audioStart": 311.802,
      "spokenStart": 311.966,
      "spokenEnd": 317.374,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第四步是真实核验。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.944,
      "audioStart": 317.374,
      "spokenStart": 317.534,
      "spokenEnd": 318.671,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "打开证据，对齐判断，检查范围和例外并记录结果。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.32,
      "audioStart": 318.611,
      "spokenStart": 318.771,
      "spokenEnd": 322.286,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c06-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "引用只有真正支持所依赖的文字才有价值。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 322.225,
      "spokenStart": 322.386,
      "spokenEnd": 325.061,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第五步是行动风险。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.944,
      "audioStart": 325.062,
      "spokenStart": 325.221,
      "spokenEnd": 326.367,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "决定结果可以自动继续、需要澄清、必须人工批准，还是因证据不足而停止。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.832,
      "audioStart": 326.315,
      "spokenStart": 326.467,
      "spokenEnd": 331.502,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第六步是反馈。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 331.504,
      "spokenStart": 331.662,
      "spokenEnd": 332.512,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "把失败判断、缺失工具或误导评分保存为新测试，让智能体和它的评测一起改进。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.624,
      "audioStart": 332.445,
      "spokenStart": 332.612,
      "spokenEnd": 338.424,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：第一，先判断可答性，再整理关键判断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.44,
      "audioStart": 338.426,
      "spokenStart": 338.584,
      "spokenEnd": 342.218,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，定义并核验清楚的证据标准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.048,
      "audioStart": 342.22,
      "spokenStart": 342.378,
      "spokenEnd": 344.621,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，把不确定性连接到行动门槛和新测试。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.032,
      "audioStart": 344.623,
      "spokenStart": 344.781,
      "spokenEnd": 348.013,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "AI 智能体幻觉不只是神秘故障，而是不确定生成遇上了奖励回答、惩罚未知的激励。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 6.432,
      "audioStart": 348.028,
      "spokenStart": 348.193,
      "spokenEnd": 353.823,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一，检查问题是否可答，再评价答案。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.408,
      "audioStart": 353.823,
      "spokenStart": 353.983,
      "spokenEnd": 356.601,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，区分已确认事实、推断和未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.408,
      "audioStart": 356.603,
      "spokenStart": 356.761,
      "spokenEnd": 359.369,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，用直接证据和独立核验检查高风险判断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.128,
      "audioStart": 359.371,
      "spokenStart": 359.529,
      "spokenEnd": 362.863,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "使用 AI 智能体不确定性与事实核验清单，设定证据门槛、选择行动边界，并把失败保存为新测试。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 7.776,
      "audioStart": 362.861,
      "spokenStart": 363.023,
      "spokenEnd": 370.012,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "目标不是让智能体听起来更不自信，而是让每份自信都先获得影响决策的资格。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.832,
      "audioStart": 370.008,
      "spokenStart": 370.172,
      "spokenEnd": 375.203,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
